<Link id="l00094" /><CodeLine lineNumber="94"><span class="doxyHighlight">        </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// be included in the ImageBase calculation.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00095" /><CodeLine lineNumber="95"><span class="doxyHighlight">        </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (Section.getLoadAddress() != 0)</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00097" /><CodeLine lineNumber="97"><span class="doxyHighlight">    &#125;</span></CodeLine>
